@NODE Introduction "MailTime Hypertext Manual - Introduction"

@{u}Introduction@{uu}
MailTime displays the time needed to send (snail) mail to another country.
It is based upon data from Price Waterhouse, which was published in a newspaper here in Luxembourg.

@ENDNODE

